/**
 *  \page   tests_page Verification and testing
 *  \tableofcontents
 *
 *
 *
 *  \section    test_overview Coverage overview
 *  All key system components are covered by unit tests using the Google Test framework.
 *  The tests are divided into logical subsystems:
 *
 *  - \ref logging_tests "Logging component tests"
 *  - Detailed flat list of all project test cases: **[Test List](\ref test)**
 *
 *
 *
 *  \section    test_run Build and run tests
 *  Building and running tests are performed in a standard manner via CTest or
 *  by directly executing the test binary:
 *
 *  \code{.sh}
 *  # Build the project and run tests
 *  make debug/test
 *
 *  # Run tests and generate an XML report
 *  ./build_debug/test/ut_logging_wrapper --gtest_output=xml:report.xml
 *  \endcode
 */
